{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-generic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/b1-english-for-developers/learn-common-phrasal-verbs-and-idioms/dialogue-2-interface-security-review","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"assignments":["<p>Gledaj video.</p>"],"bilibiliIds":null,"block":"learn-common-phrasal-verbs-and-idioms","challengeType":21,"description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Pogledajte video ispod da biste razumeli kontekst sledećih lekcija.</p>\n</section>","nodules":null,"explanation":null,"helpCategory":"English","instructions":"","fields":{"slug":"/learn/b1-english-for-developers/learn-common-phrasal-verbs-and-idioms/dialogue-2-interface-security-review"},"questions":[],"scene":{"setup":{"background":"company2-center.png","characters":[{"character":"Linda","position":{"x":-25,"y":0,"z":1},"opacity":null},{"character":"Jake","position":{"x":125,"y":0,"z":1},"opacity":null}],"audio":{"filename":"B1_24-2.mp3","startTime":1,"startTimestamp":0,"finishTimestamp":99.88},"alwaysShowDialogue":true},"commands":[{"background":null,"character":"Linda","position":{"x":25,"y":0,"z":1},"opacity":null,"startTime":0,"finishTime":null,"dialogue":null},{"background":null,"character":"Jake","position":{"x":70,"y":0,"z":1},"opacity":null,"startTime":0.5,"finishTime":null,"dialogue":null},{"background":null,"character":"Linda","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":1,"finishTime":6.54,"dialogue":{"text":"Hi, Jake. I've been looking at our current interface and thinking we could really improve how it guides users on security.","align":"left"}},{"background":null,"character":"Linda","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":6.92,"finishTime":8.84,"dialogue":{"text":"I think it's vital that we make these updates.","align":"left"}},{"background":null,"character":"Jake","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":9.62,"finishTime":17.58,"dialogue":{"text":"Absolutely. A clear interface can significantly reduce user errors that lead to security issues. What areas are you thinking about specifically?","align":"right"}},{"background":null,"character":"Linda","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":18.2,"finishTime":24.96,"dialogue":{"text":"First off, the password creation screen. We need to make the instructions clearer and more prominent. Users often overlook them.","align":"left"}},{"background":null,"character":"Jake","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":25.42,"finishTime":33.7,"dialogue":{"text":"I like that. We could use tooltips or visual indicators to show password strength. It would help users understand what makes a password strong.","align":"right"}},{"background":null,"character":"Linda","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":34.32,"finishTime":38.52,"dialogue":{"text":"I'll take note of that. I also want to address the security questions for password recovery.","align":"left"}},{"background":null,"character":"Linda","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":38.9,"finishTime":42.6,"dialogue":{"text":"They're a bit predictable. Maybe we can allow users to create their own questions?","align":"left"}},{"background":null,"character":"Jake","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":43.04,"finishTime":51.06,"dialogue":{"text":"Custom questions could be a great improvement for security. We could make the UI prompt users so that their questions are unique but memorable.","align":"right"}},{"background":null,"character":"Linda","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":51.82,"finishTime":58.68,"dialogue":{"text":"Agreed. Another thing on my list is the warning messages for suspicious activities. They need to be more immediate and convey urgency.","align":"left"}},{"background":null,"character":"Jake","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":59.24,"finishTime":68,"dialogue":{"text":"Hmm... We could try to integrate real-time alerts with more intuitive graphics. Maybe a pop-up that requires immediate user action before they can proceed?","align":"right"}},{"background":null,"character":"Linda","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":68.56,"finishTime":75.14,"dialogue":{"text":"Exactly. That should grab their attention. Lastly, about phishing. Any thoughts on how we can educate users through the interface?","align":"left"}},{"background":null,"character":"Jake","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":75.74,"finishTime":83.28,"dialogue":{"text":"We could incorporate an interactive quiz during the onboarding process. It could teach users how to recognize and handle potential phishing attempts.","align":"right"}},{"background":null,"character":"Linda","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":83.98,"finishTime":87.42,"dialogue":{"text":"That's an excellent suggestion. It's educational and engaging.","align":"left"}},{"background":null,"character":"Linda","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":87.78,"finishTime":91.84,"dialogue":{"text":"I'll draft some preliminary designs for these changes, and send them over for your feedback.","align":"left"}},{"background":null,"character":"Jake","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":92.1,"finishTime":98.46,"dialogue":{"text":"Looking forward to it. Thanks for this, Linda. It's going to make a big difference in how users interact with our system securely.","align":"right"}},{"background":null,"character":"Linda","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":98.96,"finishTime":100.88,"dialogue":{"text":"Thanks, Jake. I appreciate your input.","align":"left"}},{"background":null,"character":"Jake","position":{"x":125,"y":0,"z":1},"opacity":null,"startTime":101.38,"finishTime":null,"dialogue":null},{"background":null,"character":"Linda","position":{"x":-25,"y":0,"z":1},"opacity":null,"startTime":101.88,"finishTime":null,"dialogue":null}]},"superBlock":"b1-english-for-developers","tests":[],"title":"Dijalog 2: Pregled bezbednosti interfejsa","transcript":null,"translationPending":false,"videoId":null,"videoLocaleIds":null}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/b1-english-for-developers/#learn-common-phrasal-verbs-and-idioms","dashedName":"dialogue-2-interface-security-review","certification":"b1-english-for-developers","disableLoopProtectTests":false,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"b1-english-for-developers","chapter":null,"module":null,"block":"learn-common-phrasal-verbs-and-idioms","isFirstStep":false,"template":null,"required":[],"isLastChallengeInBlock":false,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/b1-english-for-developers/learn-common-phrasal-verbs-and-idioms/task-49","prevChallengePath":"/learn/b1-english-for-developers/learn-common-phrasal-verbs-and-idioms/task-48","id":"685437dac4e8b5e48a696f70","saveSubmissionToDB":null},"projectPreview":{"challengeData":{"challengeType":19,"challengeFiles":[]}},"id":"/learn/b1-english-for-developers/learn-common-phrasal-verbs-and-idioms/dialogue-2-interface-security-review"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3858520367"],"slicesMap":{}}